{"tid":1275634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住，因為我已經冇辦法再相信香港政府","createTime":"2019-07-01T21:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:50:20.000Z","uid":225822,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"27242068d621c97931831e93e031489446d2932f","tid":1275634,"uid":225822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:10:36.000Z","msg":"經過今日之後，我發現就算我係一個香港人，但香港已經唔再屬於我。<br />\n<br />\n我相信眼見為實，我曾經發夢出過去，見到各種屬於香港人嘅人情味，真係喊咗出黎，每個出黎嘅人都會為其他人專登做多一步，為嘅唔係自己，而係其他人，同香港嘅未來，我真係好感動，而且非常之感謝大家，你地先係真正嘅香港人，而唔係為錢為自己嘅垃圾廢老賤種。<br />\n<br />\n我以為經過今日之後，大家立法會都入埋，應該會逼到政府回應，但原來唔係，佢地繼續講佢地想講嘅野，講廢老想聽嘅野，為嘅就係保住自己嘅飯碗同面子，我覺得自己已經再冇辦法面對呢個香港政府。<br />\n<br />\n官員問責制？WFC。<br />\n五大訴求？關我撚事。<br />\n黑警濫權？吹咩。<br />\n撐警廢老打人？咁又點。<br />\n<br />\n當一切擺到眼前嘅時候，原來係咁難以接受，我曾經以為我接受到呢種荒謬，但原來我做唔到，係呢個六月，我個心已經死咗無數次，的確要多謝香港政府。<br />\n<br />\n係今日之後，係佔領立法會之後，所有野已經返唔到轉頭，之後更荒謬嘅陸續有黎，我希望咁多位可以保重，保持住真正香港人嘅精神。<br />\n<br />\n而我，已經攰了。"},{"pid":"1f2992dbbcca68b21abaf36460bbf496024de0e4","tid":1275634,"uid":226955,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:11:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">林鄭玩緊共匪老技倆，拉籠一派打一派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派五毛做打手，屌嗰啲當然90%都係五毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉籠一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，民初時期國民政府分裂就係共匪搞出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次佢不斷鬧示威者暴力，就係想聽朝班三姑六婆一齊鬧埋一份，造成世代之爭，呢個就係拉籠一派打一派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪玩咗咁多年分化，普羅大眾應該要熟悉呢一點，大家都係擁抱自由民主嘅價值，呢個要保持頭腦清晰，同伴之間要互相尊重，唔好咁易中咗政府同五毛嘅計"},{"pid":"cf09dff54a76c4aa4be98a9c511ad4a788c21d3c","tid":1275634,"uid":261396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9a40b34aa241085080c4b01cdb253c776954e1","tid":1275634,"uid":154486,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:14:12.000Z","msg":"攰就抖下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e14b0d01586f8bd32c3d271544b24779ae9ea64","tid":1275634,"uid":40718,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:14:33.000Z","msg":"頂住 大家齊上齊落 一個都不能少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf46fe2f0091d67e5cf83d4d8e9b19a6b022aa7","tid":1275634,"uid":23090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:14:59.000Z","msg":"一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c918e4ed252326f1efec8a9249bd8728ed85fc7","tid":1275634,"uid":226955,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:15:17.000Z","msg":"樓主唔洗灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，宜家台灣同好多外國輿論都好支持香港人，場波伸有排踢<br />\n<br />\n另外，有歷史定律嘅存在，喺大家都有去為民主自由而努力嘅前題之下，其實係一定會贏，只係我地唔知道幾時先會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋過程都好可能會有好多挫折。至於點解會贏，原因好簡單，因為呢個係人類歷史發展嘅必然趨勢，舉個例，起初人類係原始部落社會，後來就演變成封建君主專制社會，歐洲啟蒙之後神權至上受到挑戰，慢慢衝破思想框框，思想同科技得以進步，後來民主思潮萌生，將一個又一個君主專制政權推倒，最後席捲全球，所以全球民主化其實係歷史發展嘅必然，前題係必須大家都要去為民主自由而努力，正如呢幾百年嘅人一樣，冇佢地嘅努力都唔會令民主得以喺世界擴散"},{"pid":"af961e48b831fa984f7803cd226bdb3e2bf1977c","tid":1275634,"uid":245484,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:16:13.000Z","msg":"攰就訓下覺好喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好長眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc6cfae94778403c3b6a087cf50e99b7906fee6","tid":1275634,"uid":150742,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:17:23.000Z","msg":"攰咪抖下，等我去接力頂住先，好快冇事架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f466e734b5f3d164df8c9990fe171566cf98349a","tid":1275634,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:17:24.000Z","msg":"【廣傳】所有出現過喺現場嘅義士，見到呢個post 即刻更改Facebook私隱設定，尤其係相！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275626</a>"},{"pid":"5a6d78bc189373001c304593255d3e8d57ad69be","tid":1275634,"uid":89223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:20:40.000Z","msg":"政府一心 同香港人決戰 但我想講咁只會官逼民反 幫我哋種下革命的基礎"},{"pid":"fc09453600307cba7354f823f803c0dda400b86b","tid":1275634,"uid":205566,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:22:18.000Z","msg":"抖吓囉<br />\n政治一晚就搞得掂，其他國家就唔洗買軍艦大砲啦"},{"pid":"d27977f73441680bff5e79c138f8818ea7623a4f","tid":1275634,"uid":192971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:23:02.000Z","msg":"[黑旗已升] 大家快D諗清楚 宣布成立臨時政府/獨立vs繼續沉默?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PJsLvU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PJsLvU</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aaa305ad1502996a6b86000253d13a3d555218f","tid":1275634,"uid":115500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:25:18.000Z","msg":"抖下先，巴打加油！"},{"pid":"89c4ed693475ecf6bf2144d299bf445c0a13e909","tid":1275634,"uid":261043,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:28:03.000Z","msg":"我都好憎香港，但好愛香港人呀<br />\n<br />\n巴打好好休息，建國之日我地要一齊慶祝"},{"pid":"39c709b0bcfdc8f6c8ca0fecbd6835552194d468","tid":1275634,"uid":225822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:44:18.000Z","msg":"對住呢個政府，我真係覺得好撚攰。<br />\n諗起陳健波話自己收成期，就仲更加灰。<br />\n屌你老母，我收成期都未到，香港政府點解要破壞我嘅耕耘期？"},{"pid":"f6753b7aef6c59baecf42ba34ce431759b4c0210","tid":1275634,"uid":248146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39c709b0bcfdc8f6c8ca0fecbd6835552194d468","tid":1275634,"uid":225822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:44:18.000Z","msg":"對住呢個政府，我真係覺得好撚攰。<br />\n諗起陳健波話自己收成期，就仲更加灰。<br />\n屌你老母，我收成期都未到，香港政府點解要破壞我嘅耕耘期？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:57:49.000Z","msg":"我地要珍惜響耕耘期有咁多同伴！<br />\n我好相信絕處逢生，灰一陣好喇！<br />\n攰就休息下喇。"},{"pid":"ad6a1eff6b7eb165f723bc03732618fd5ee6b5fa","tid":1275634,"uid":43413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXUWQYC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXUWQYC.png&h=48d247dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a16e4b6482c5ab5ba0a42d6924095d9bbe8287e","tid":1275634,"uid":172051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:08:34.000Z","msg":"抖下 再黎過 我地需要你 唔好放棄我地 唔好放棄香港 我地互相撐住好無"},{"pid":"6d689f632741820ef1ad0df7baa5041b6aba22ed","tid":1275634,"uid":37713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:09:48.000Z","msg":"巴打巴打<br />\n夜啦<br />\n攰既攤上床好好瞓一覺好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果有說話想講可以係到講<br />\n大家會陪你 會明白你 會聽你講架<br />\n<br />\n我地唔想再失去任何一位手足<br />\n你唔好講到好似...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb57c9cc89344103913ea07fa6fe5d40d84ad35","tid":1275634,"uid":212706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:16:11.000Z","msg":"攰就休一休，而家要做好輿論戰"},{"pid":"b6ac772ac8169c6ba3ab7a8579d7d9d27825024f","tid":1275634,"uid":34602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:16:22.000Z","msg":"其實唔理你係正常，佢地有無得做都唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0623f475e18f19c610eb29559007b702b193ece8","tid":1275634,"uid":2307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:18:06.000Z","msg":"休息一下再重新出發"},{"pid":"e5ad1936a552a72fdeee1567dc310b1dbb8b4f0a","tid":1275634,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:18:20.000Z","msg":"仆街<br />\n而家發夢齊齊出去，齊齊番黎　<br />\n大家平安冇事<br />\n你唔係咁樣先黎放棄呀？<br />\n說好的齊上齊落？　一齊走？"},{"pid":"15d481af7e46ad88ce3a0b8bedc485ccd1ce35e6","tid":1275634,"uid":56063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,